# Demo Data Specification

## Fleet Composition

### Dubai Metro Fleet (Total: 128 trains)

#### Kinki Sharyo Fleet (49 trains)
- **ID Pattern**: KS-001 to KS-049
- **In Service Since**: 2009 (Red Line launch)
- **Configuration**: 5-car sets
- **Primary Lines**: Red Line

#### Alstom Metropolis Fleet (79 trains)
- **ID Pattern**: AL-001 to AL-079
- **Batches**:
  - AL-001 to AL-050: Original Green Line fleet (2011)
  - AL-051 to AL-079: Route 2020 expansion (2020)
- **Configuration**: 5-car sets (compatible with Kinki fleet)
- **Primary Lines**: Green Line + Red Line (Route 2020)

---

## Maintenance Hierarchy

### Preventive Maintenance Types

| Code | Name | Interval | Duration | Tracks | Concurrent Limit |
|------|------|----------|----------|--------|------------------|
| A1 | Light Inspection | 14 days | 4 hours | Any | Unlimited |
| A2 | Standard Inspection | 28 days | 8 hours | Any | Unlimited |
| B | Minor Overhaul | 180 days | 72 hours (3 days) | Any | 6 max |
| C | Major Overhaul | 730 days (2 years) | 336 hours (14 days) | Specialized | 2 max |
| D | Complete Rebuild | 2190 days (6 years) | 1008 hours (42 days) | Specialized | 1 max |

### Corrective Maintenance
- **Unplanned**: Triggered by failures or inspections
- **Priority Levels**: P1 (Critical), P2 (Urgent), P3 (Normal)
- **Impact on Schedule**: May preempt planned maintenance

---

## Maintenance Depot Layout

### Track Configuration (8 tracks total)

| Track | Type | Compatible Fleet | Capacity | Equipment |
|-------|------|------------------|----------|-----------|
| T1 | Heavy | Kinki Sharyo | 1 train | Lifting jacks, wheel lathe |
| T2 | Heavy | Kinki Sharyo | 1 train | Lifting jacks, bogie drop |
| T3 | Light | Kinki Sharyo | 2 trains | Inspection pits |
| T4 | Light | Universal | 2 trains | Inspection pits |
| T5 | Light | Alstom | 2 trains | Inspection pits |
| T6 | Heavy | Alstom | 1 train | Lifting jacks, wheel lathe |
| T7 | Heavy | Alstom | 1 train | Lifting jacks, bogie drop |
| T8 | Specialized | Universal | 1 train | Paint booth, deep clean |

### Constraints
- **C/D Overhauls**: Require Heavy tracks (T1, T2, T6, T7)
- **A/B Maintenance**: Can use Light or Heavy tracks
- **Fleet Compatibility**: Kinki uses T1-T4, Alstom uses T4-T8, Universal = T4, T8

